{"tid":2046428,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"英倫辦公室（34）光復香港 時代革命","createTime":"2020-06-01T11:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T13:50:14.000Z","uid":85444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e173153ee479190ea4abf5f2145c223c34261473","tid":2046428,"uid":85444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"Visa<br />\nTier 5 (Youth Mobility Scheme) visa - Also known as working holiday<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/tier-5-youth-mobility\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Ftier-5-youth-mobility&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=d3653f8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/tier-5-youth-mobility</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/forumdisplay.php?f=300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.backpackers.com.tw%2Fforum%2Fforumdisplay.php%3Ff%3D300&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=fd2bc422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/forumdisplay.php?f=300</a><br />\nBNO &gt;&gt; HKSAR<br />\nIf you&rsquo;re applying this visa using HKSAR passport. You need to be sponsored with an annual quota of 1000.<br />\n<br />\nTier 2 (General - Working)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/tier-2-general\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Ftier-2-general&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=a2a767c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/tier-2-general</a><br />\n<br />\nFor Settlement - Permanent Residence/Indefinite Leave to Remain (ILR)<br />\nOption 1<br />\nIf you have been living in UK for 10 years and met certain requirements<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/long-residence/eligibility\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Flong-residence%2Feligibility&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=b34fbc47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/long-residence/eligibility</a><br />\nOption 2<br />\nIf you have been living and working (under Tier 2) in the UK for 5 years and met certain requirements<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/settle-in-the-uk/y/you-have-a-work-visa/tier-2-general-visa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fsettle-in-the-uk%2Fy%2Fyou-have-a-work-visa%2Ftier-2-general-visa&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=4e80e7bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/settle-in-the-uk/y/you-have-a-work-visa/tier-2-general-visa</a><br />\n<br />\nHousing<br />\n<a href=\"http://Rightmove.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FRightmove.com&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=b370f725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Rightmove.com</a><br />\n<br />\nDriving<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/apply-first-provisional-driving-licence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fapply-first-provisional-driving-licence&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=d5e464a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/apply-first-provisional-driving-licence</a><br />\nExchange your driving licence<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/dvlaforms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fdvlaforms&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=96fc983b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/dvlaforms</a><br />\n<br />\nLiving Cost<br />\nLondon/Cambridge - Same as Hong Kong<br />\nOutside the above metropolitan area, and the rest of the UK - cheaper than Hong Kong<br />\nSee more below<br />\n<br />\nFAQ 1:<br />\nI need English C2 level to get a job.<br />\nNope you don't, B2 is doable.<br />\n<br />\nFAQ 2:<br />\nA smaller firm is more likely to help with visa issues.<br />\nNo, not likely at all.<br />\n<br />\nFAQ 3:<br />\nTier 5 switch to Tier 2?<br />\nIt is possible but not going to be easy. Higher chance when your job is on the shortage list below:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/immigration-rules/immigration-rules-appendix-k-shortage-occupation-list\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fguidance%2Fimmigration-rules%2Fimmigration-rules-appendix-k-shortage-occupation-list&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=045618d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/guidance/immigration-rules/immigration-rules-appendix-k-shortage-occupation-list</a><br />\n<br />\nFAQ 4:<br />\nTier 4 to Tier 2?<br />\nPreparing it when you are in year 2.<br />\n<br />\nFAQ 5:<br />\nTier 2/4/5 to settlement immediately?<br />\nDefinitively possible if you are a single girl, or boy?<br />\nLevae your tg/ig here with your sexual orientation and a picture. Our 手足 will contact you shortly.<br />\n<br />\nMore Ref:<br />\nOnline supermarket: <a href=\"http://ocado.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Focado.com&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=7fb9ce00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ocado.com</a><br />\nChinese grocery: <a href=\"http://wingyip.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwingyip.com&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=0a2cb903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">wingyip.com</a>, <a href=\"http://loonfung.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Floonfung.com&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=3b8d6005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">loonfung.com</a><br />\nCheaper Utilities &amp; Insurance: <a href=\"http://uswitch.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fuswitch.com&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=835eccf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">uswitch.com</a>, <a href=\"http://comparethemarket.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcomparethemarket.com&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=76c442cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">compa